title: Real.Housewives.of.Melbourne.s01e06.PDTV.x264.Hector.mp4
description:
Anyone For Tennis?: Lydia's studying design at RMIT and shows the other students how it's done. Andrea's alarmed at the slow building progress at the new Liberty Belle Skin Centre given she's planning a launch party and Janet's reworking her increasingly expensive renovations at Red Hill. Andrea hosts a tennis day at her luxury beach house on the Mornington Peninsula. Everything starts off swimmingly but its game, set and match when one of the girls arrives late. Jackie suggests a late night salsa lesson to diffuse the tension but will it prove healing?
If you see "Hector" on the end of a file it means I capped it.
Enjoy, Gaz/Hector :)
